{"title":"Centos基本命令","uid":"b15cc88af71ece54b6070d7a06d99d7c","slug":"Centos基本命令","date":"2022-07-21T05:02:11.000Z","updated":"2022-07-21T05:17:58.307Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Centos基本命令.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<link rel=\"stylesheet\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-style-marker\" href=\"\\assets\\css\\APlayer.min.css\"><script src=\"\\assets\\js\\APlayer.min.js\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-script-marker\"></script><h2 id=\"vim的使用：\"><a href=\"#vim的使用：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"vim的使用：\"></a>vim的使用：</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">yum install vim -y</code></pre>\n\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>x</th>\n<th>保存退出</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>q</td>\n<td>退出，不保存</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>q！</td>\n<td>强制退出，不保存</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>w</td>\n<td>保存，但没退出</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>wq</td>\n<td>保存并退出</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>wq！</td>\n<td>强制保存并退出</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2 id=\"配置网卡：\"><a href=\"#配置网卡：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"配置网卡：\"></a>配置网卡：</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">vim &#x2F;etc&#x2F;sysconfig&#x2F;network-scripts&#x2F;ifcfg-ens33（以实际网卡为准，可以用Tab补全）\n#编辑网卡配置文件\nTYPE&#x3D;Ethernet\n#网卡类型\nPROXY_METHOD&#x3D;none\nBROWSER_ONLY&#x3D;no\nBOOTPROTO&#x3D;static\n#网卡获取IP地址的协议（dhcp&#x2F;static）\nDEFROUTE&#x3D;yes\n#是否启动默认路由\nIPV4_FAILURE_FATAL&#x3D;no\nNAME&#x3D;ens33\n#网卡名称\nUUID&#x3D;ab2faa71-3836-42cb-bf9b-b56bbc8c31bd\nDEVICE&#x3D;ens33\n#网卡名称\nONBOOT&#x3D;yes\n#设置开机启动网卡\nDNS1&#x3D;x.x.x.x\n#DNS\nIPADDR&#x3D;x.x.x.x\n#网卡IP地址\nNETMASK&#x3D;x.x.x.x\n#子网掩码\nGATEWAY&#x3D;x.x.x.x\n#默认网关IP地址\n</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"防火墙：\"><a href=\"#防火墙：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"防火墙：\"></a>防火墙：</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">Systemctl  disable  firewalld.service   开机禁止防火墙自动启动\nsystemctl start firewalld.service        启动防火墙\nsystemctl enable firewalld.service      开机自动启动防火墙\nsystemctl   status  firewalld.service   查看防火墙状态</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"selinux：\"><a href=\"#selinux：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"selinux：\"></a>selinux：</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">getenforce \t\t获取当前selinux状态\nsetenforce 0\t临时关闭selinux</code></pre>\n\n","text":"vim的使用：yum install vim -y x 保存退出 q 退出，不保存 q！ 强制退出，不保存 w 保存，但没退出 wq 保存并退出 wq！ 强制保存并退出 配置网卡：vim &#x2F;etc&#x2F;sysconfig&#x2F;network-scripts&...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":872,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Centos","slug":"Centos","count":7,"path":"api/categories/Centos.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Centos","slug":"Centos","count":6,"path":"api/tags/Centos.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#vim%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%9A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">vim的使用：</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%BD%91%E5%8D%A1%EF%BC%9A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">配置网卡：</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%98%B2%E7%81%AB%E5%A2%99%EF%BC%9A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">防火墙：</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#selinux%EF%BC%9A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">selinux：</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"H-MiKing","slug":"h-miking","avatar":"https://s2.loli.net/2022/03/09/hnWbjs6yMGKDXdk.jpg","link":"/","description":"新手博客，在校大学生，曾获得某省技能大赛一等奖。","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/H-MiKing","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/hjsuo","csdn":"https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_51369125?spm=1000.2115.3001.5343","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"/svg/bilibili.svg","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/346448962?spm_id_from=333.1007.0.0"}}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"磁盘管理","uid":"620790019ebf6e